{"tid":2369077,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"浸聯會牧函轟大搜捕　籲為真理長期爭戰","createTime":"2021-01-16T18:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T09:40:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":85,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8b67bae9edfbe3929bba7b3ffa1aaba3cef8e5","tid":2369077,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/koA1GywoEgPg9zRODWBk_o0t82A=/802x1306/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PG5XC5UMEVGRLEJ6B73DOQRMIQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkoA1GywoEgPg9zRODWBk_o0t82A%3D%2F802x1306%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPG5XC5UMEVGRLEJ6B73DOQRMIQ.gif&h=2ed1735f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YPCV1eQjdE2yMsyPy7A7SRoga7A=/802x609/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MU6DSB5PWJHC5DB7B4UWBTM2ZQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYPCV1eQjdE2yMsyPy7A7SRoga7A%3D%2F802x609%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMU6DSB5PWJHC5DB7B4UWBTM2ZQ.gif&h=e2dbcfea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eowYb52Hafx-URnubsPuf7lxy1I=/802x581/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WG3YDMDZVRB7XNGQ4UY3K3CHOE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeowYb52Hafx-URnubsPuf7lxy1I%3D%2F802x581%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWG3YDMDZVRB7XNGQ4UY3K3CHOE.gif&h=b94999d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年年中刮起的寒流，一直沒停下來，我城一片肅殺。55名泛民因參與立法會初選被指控顛覆國家政權，三位關注社會的牧者在基督教媒體時代論壇發表牧函回應，勉勵弟兄姊妹繼續追求公義和真理。其中香港浸信會聯會會長羅慶才牧師說：「真理與虛假之戰，是長期的爭戰。我們必須要忍耐，惟有忍耐到底，才能得見其成就。」<br />\n<br />\n羅慶才在牧函中指出，剛踏入2021年，一種肅殺的氣氛就如濃霧一般將我們籠罩着。有53名曾策劃及參與去年民主派初選的人士在同一天被捕，此事猶如一顆「震撼彈」在人群中，在毫無心理準備的情況下引爆一樣。毫無疑問，這行動是經過精心策劃及部署，以製造最大的震懾效果。<br />\n<br />\n另一位牧師袁天佑形容，國安法是架在市民頸項上的刀，任由當權者解讀，壓制異見人士。他引述電影《四大名捕》對白：「有光的地方，總會有黑影」、「有黑影的地方，總會有光照着」。他指這兩句對白道出世界有暗有光的事實，問題只是從哪個角度去看。前者會從灰暗的角度看事物，後者從積極的角度來看事物，帶來光明的力量和盼望。<br />\n<br />\n蒲錦昌牧師則說：「香港如烏雲密佈，大風暴快要來臨的一刻：更可怖的恐怕還在後頭。」但他引述經文與教徒共勉：「平安的日子其實是人生的特例，考驗和困厄才是生命的常態。凡跟從耶穌基督的人，也要準備和祂一同受苦，才能與祂一同得享榮耀。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/O77XHG6JFRC2JP65PX43MMQS3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FO77XHG6JFRC2JP65PX43MMQS3U%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHMSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=95c33f72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FO77XHG6JFRC2JP65PX43MMQS3U%2F&h=31d4032d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/O77XHG6JFRC2JP65PX43MMQS3U/</a>"},{"pid":"9459d2d1a280b21e20168d6ee2b51a50886696fb","tid":2369077,"uid":59408,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:53:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係人話<br />\n羅牧師直係搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姓共會班仆街高層<br />\n冚家落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b40eca45e1c7674155bebb614d57c0d191d5e7","tid":2369077,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9459d2d1a280b21e20168d6ee2b51a50886696fb","tid":2369077,"uid":59408,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:53:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係人話<br />\n羅牧師直係搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姓共會班仆街高層<br />\n冚家落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/